    "Table 11 presents the results of pairwise comparisons of the number of misrepresentations per story across the three language resource groups (high, mid, and low).",
    "For each pair, the median difference, effect size (Cliff's 𝛿), and associated 𝑝-value are reported.",
    "Statistically significant differences (𝑝 <.001) are indicated with double asterisks (**).",
    "Table 12 summarizes the pairwise comparisons of misrepresentation counts across regions of different tiers.",
    "Statistics for comparison of misrepresentation counts between open-source and closed modelsFig. 2.2Fig."
